data.description: Experience the charm of living North of the River in the popular Rock Quarry school zone for a great price! In 2022, this home underwent a comprehensive renovation. Upgrades include a new Roof, HVAC, Sheetrock, Interior & Exterior Paint, Kitchen Appliances, Double-Pane Windows, Gutters, Doors, Lighting Fixtures, Slick Ceilings, Kitchen & Bathroom tile, Soft-close Cabinetry, & LVP flooring. Luxurious finishes like a custom spice cabinet, farmhouse sink, and granite add a modern touch. A tankless hot water heater ensures you'll never run out of hot water. A newly added covered patio & a level, fully fenced backyard, make a delightful space for outdoor activities. Don't miss out on this beautiful home - come see it soon!
